data.description: Everyday is a vacation in this spacious home for everyone! This beautiful home boasts a 3-way Split Plan Bedrooms great for privacy, 10' ceilings,  with the fourth bedroom located in its own wing of the house.The gorgeous backyard oasis boasts a crystal blue pool and spa, a covered porch and screened lanai overlooking a serene pond with the kitchen and family room just steps away from your lanai. This home chef's dream kitchen includes an island, double-door pantry, smooth-top range, microwave, tile floors and much more! The owner's bedroom suite enjoys ample space and beautiful views of an exterior escape through sliding glass doors, complete with an oversized walk-in closet, a larger-than-normal shower and a lovely garden tub. Newer roof, air conditioner and numerous updates throughout this home makes it just right for the new owner. Lexington Oaks is an 18-hole golf course community with a golf club and restaurant, also includes a rec center, park, playground, 2 swimming pools, and a day care center. Enjoy living in this beautiful landscaped community with lower Pasco County taxes.  This community is conveniently located near I75, Wiregrass Mall, Shopping, Restaurants, and downtown Tampa. You will love this triple Split Floor Plan and the ample square feet, with so many areas to retreat to if privacy is what you seek.
